oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Railroad track profile, French railroads on which Sgt. Harry C. Woods worked as conductor
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Track profile showing 4 lines: Clamecy - Cosne, Laroche - Clamecy, Laroche - Nuits-sous-Ravieres, and Nuits-sous-Ravieres - Chatillon-sur-Seine. Sgt. Harry C. Woods was employed as an American soldier on these lines and had served as railroad conductor before the war. He was assigned to Co. A, 76th Regt., 16th Guard Div.
